name: Alfa Pilot’s Club
about: Alfa Pilots Club, located in Kaunas, Lithuania, offers comprehensive airplane flight training. Situated at the Kauno aleksotas S. Dariaus ir S. Gireno airport (EYKS), the school provides a professional and supportive environment for aspiring pilots. With a dedicated team and modern facilities, Alfa Pilots Club ensures high-quality training, preparing students for successful careers in aviation. For inquiries, contact us at +370 61126064 or email info@pilotai.lt. Join Alfa Pilots Club to take the first step towards your flying career.
